translations: 不结果实的；未播种的；非种子的

sentences.sentence: Venus was the first unseeded woman in history to reach the final round.
sentences.translation: 维纳斯是历史上第一个进入最后一轮的女性非种子选手。

sentences.sentence: The first seed lost to an unseeded player by 2-6 in the first round.
sentences.translation: 头号种子选手在第一轮就以2比6负于一名非种子选手。

sentences.sentence: Any unseeded torrents will be deleted on sight regardless of the reason.
sentences.translation: 任何的被不播种的奔流将会不管理由在视力上划除。
